### 新增用户 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
  "age": 25
}


### 新增用户 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "lisi",
  "email": "lisi@example.com",
  "age": 24
}


### 新增用户 (POST)（年龄超限，应返回400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "somebody",
  "email": "somebody@example.com",
  "age": 200
}


### 查询用户 (GET)(第一次 会查数据库并存入Redis)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

### 查询用户 (GET)(第二次 应该直接从Redis返回，控制台无SQL输出)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1


### 查询用户 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/2


### 查询用户 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/3


### 修改用户 (PUT)(会清除Redis缓存)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 2,
  "username": "changed",
  "email": "lisi@example.com",
  "age": 24
}

### 再次查询该用户（修改后第一次查，会重新查数据库并缓存）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/2


### 新增用户 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangwu",
  "email": "zhangwu@example.com",
  "age": 25
}


### 分页查询（第1页，每页2条，无关键字）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/page?page=1&size=2

### 分页查询（第2页，每页2条）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/page?page=2&size=2

### 分页查询 + 关键字模糊匹配
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/page?page=1&size=5&keyword=zhang


### 查看所有用户 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### 删除用户 (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

### 再次查询已删除用户（返回404）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1